## Tips
- Local Ignore:  echo YOURFILE_OR_DIRECTOY >> .git/info/exclude 

		exclude file is the same as .gitignore, however it will not be pushed to the central repo
		after pulling work repos eg: apps/workApp, you can ignore it from the foundation exclude and have a separete git repo



